room_title: Escape room "Tomb of the Red Queen" by Rush Hour Live Escapes in Fredericksburg
room_address: 1 Towne Centre Boulevard, Suite 3100, Fredericksburg, VA 22407
room_description: As a team of archaeologists, you are studying the ancient Mayan ruins of Palenque. Shortly after entering the dig, you find the entrance locked behind you. King Pakal commands you to complete the burial rituals to allow the soul of his beloved wife to join him in the heavens! Can you find your way out of the temple before he arrives to have his revenge!
